      "suggested_fix": "Add a concrete deliverable: before building the parser, pull 20 diverse real documents via gabi-es (varying organs, decades, sections) and create a `tests/fixtures/dou-structure/` directory. Write the parser with these as test cases. Define an acceptance threshold: parser must correctly identify article boundaries in ≥90% of test fixtures. Documents that fail parsing get plain-text rendering with a visible 'structured view unavailable' indicator, not silent degradation. Add 2 days to the viewer timebox for parser development and test fixture creation."
